[section#exec.associate
    [`execution::associate]
]

[para]
[:en] [`associate] tries to associate a sender with an async scope such that the
scope can track the lifetime of any asynchronous operations created with the sender.
[:zh_CN] [`associate] 尝试将发送器与异步作用域关联，以便该作用域可以跟踪与发送器
一起创建的任何异步操作的生命周期。

[para]
[:en] Let [*associate-data] be the following exposition-only class template:
[:zh_CN] 令 [*associate-data] 为以下仅用于阐释的类模板：

[%@lib execution::[*associate-data]]
[codeblock:synopsis]
namespace std::execution {
  template<[[redoc("`:c>")]]scope_token Token, [[redoc("`:c>")]]sender Sender>
  struct [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data {                                               // [=expos]
    using [[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender =                                                 // [=expos]
      remove_cvref_t<decltype(declval<Token&>().wrap(declval<Sender>()))>;
    using [[redoc("*>")]]assoc-t = decltype(declval<Token&>().try_associate());        // [=expos]
    using [[redoc("*>")]]sender-ref =                                                  // [=expos]
      unique_ptr<[[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender, decltype([](auto* p) noexcept { destroy_at(p); })>;

    explicit [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data(Token t, Sender&& s)
      : [[redoc("*>")]]sndr(t.wrap(std::forward<Sender>(s))),
        [[redoc("*>")]]assoc([&] {
          [[redoc("*>")]]sender-ref guard{addressof([[redoc("*>")]]sndr)};
          auto assoc = t.try_associate();
          if (assoc) {
            guard.release();
          }
          return assoc;
        }()) {}

    [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data(const [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data& other)
      noexcept(is_nothrow_copy_constructible_v<[[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender> &&
               noexcept(other.[[redoc("*>")]]assoc.try_associate()));

    [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data([[redoc("*>")]]associate-data&& other)
      noexcept(is_nothrow_move_constructible_v<[[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender>)
      : [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data(std::move(other).release()) {}

    ~[[redoc("*>")]]associate-data();

    pair<[[redoc("*>")]]assoc-t, [[redoc("*>")]]sender-ref> release() && noexcept;

  private:
    [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data(pair<[[redoc("*>")]]assoc-t, [[redoc("*>")]]sender-ref> parts);                    // \expos
    union {
      [[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender [[redoc("*>")]]sndr;                                                 // [=expos]
    };
    [[redoc("*>")]]assoc-t [[redoc("*>")]]assoc;                                                      // [=expos]
  };

  template<[[redoc("`:c>")]]scope_token Token, [[redoc("`:c>")]]sender Sender>
    [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data(Token, Sender&&) -> [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data<Token, Sender>;
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] For an [*associate-data] object [`a], [`bool(a.[*assoc])] is [`true]
if and only if an association was successfully made and is owned by [`a].
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`*associate-data] 对象 [`a]，当且仅当成功建立了关联并且由 [`a]
拥有时，[`bool(a.[*assoc])] 为 [`true]。

[%@lib@ctor execution::[*associate-data]]
[codeblock:declaration]
[[redoc("*>")]]associate-data(const [[redoc("*>")]]associate-data& other)
  noexcept(is_nothrow_copy_constructible_v<[[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender> &&
           noexcept(other.[[redoc("*>")]]assoc.try_associate()));
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[:en] [*wrap-sender] models [`:c copy_constructible].
[:zh_CN] [*wrap-sender] 构成 [`:c copy_constructible]。

[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes [*assoc] with [`other.[*assoc].try_associate()].
[:zh_CN] 以 [`other.[*assoc].try_associate()] 初始化 [*assoc]。

[:en] If [`bool([*assoc])] is [`true], initializes [*sndr] with [`other.[*sndr]].
[:zh_CN] 若 [`bool([*assoc])] 为 [`true]，则以 [`other.[*sndr]] 初始化 [*sndr].
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor execution::[*associate-data]]
[codeblock:declaration]
[[redoc("*>")]]associate-data(pair<[[redoc("*>")]]assoc-t, [[redoc("*>")]]sender-ref> parts);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes [*assoc] with [`std::move(parts.first)].
[:zh_CN] 以 [`std::move(parts.first)] 初始化 [*assoc]。

[:en] If [`bool([*assoc])] is [`true], initializes [*sndr] with [`std::move(*parts.second)].
[:zh_CN] 若 [`bool([*assoc])] 为 [`true]，则以 [`std::move(*parts.second)] 初始化 [*sndr].
[div:end]

[%@lib@dtor execution::[*associate-data]]
[codeblock:declaration]
~[[redoc("*>")]]associate-data();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] If [`bool([*assoc])] is [`true], destroys [*sndr].
[:zh_CN] 若 [`bool([*assoc])] 为 [`true]，则销毁 [*sndr].
[div:end]

[%@lib@member release[!execution::[*associate-data]]]
[codeblock:declaration]
pair<[[redoc("*>")]]assoc-t, [[redoc("*>")]]sender-ref> release() && noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs an object [`u] of type [*sender-ref] that is initialized with
[`addressof([*sndr])] if [`bool([*assoc])] is [`true] and with [`nullptr] otherwise,
then returns [`pair{std::move([*assoc]), std::move(u)}].
[:zh_CN] 构造一个 [*sender-ref] 类型的对象 [`u]，当 [`bool([*assoc])] 为 [`true]
时以 [`addressof([*sndr])] 初始化，否则以 [`nullptr] 初始化，然后返回
[`pair{std::move([*assoc]), std::move(u)}]。
[div:end]

[para]
[:en] The name [`associate] denotes a pipeable sender adaptor object.
[:zh_CN] 名字 [`associate] 代表一个可连管道的发送器适配器对象。

[:en] For subexpressions [`sndr] and [`token]:
[:zh_CN] 对于子表达式 [`sndr] 和 [`token]：

[list]
[item]
[:en] If [`decltype((sndr))] does not satisfy [`:c sender], or
[`remove_cvref_t<decltype((token))>] does not satisfy [`:c scope_token], then
[`associate(sndr, token)] is ill-formed.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`decltype((sndr))] 不符合 [`:c sender]，或者
[`remove_cvref_t<decltype((token))>] 不符合 [`:c scope_token]，那么
[`associate(sndr, token)] 非良构。

[item]
[:en] Otherwise, the expression [`associate(sndr, token)] is expression-equivalent to
[`[*make-sender](associate, [*associate-data](token, sndr))].
[:zh_CN] 否则，表达式 [`associate(sndr, token)] 按表达式等价于
[`[*make-sender](associate, [*associate-data](token, sndr))]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] The exposition-only class template [*impls-for] ([#exec.snd.expos])
is specialized for [`associate_t] as follows:
[:zh_CN] 仅用于阐释的类模板 [*impls-for]（[#exec.snd.expos]）针对 [`associate_t] 进行如下特化：

[%@lib execution::[*impls-for]<associate_t>]
[codeblock]
namespace std::execution {
  template<>
  struct [[redoc("*>")]]impls-for<associate_t> : [[redoc("*>")]]default-impls {
    static constexpr auto [[redoc("*>")]]get-state = [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]];                // [=expos]
    static constexpr auto [[redoc("*>")]]start = [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]];                    // [=expos]

    template<class Sndr, class... Env>
      static consteval void [[redoc("*>")]]check-types() {                     // [=expos]
        using associate_data_t = remove_cvref_t<[[redoc("*>")]]data-type<Sndr>>;
        using child_type_t = associate_data_t::[[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender;
        (void)get_completion_signatures<child_type_t, [[redoc("*>")]]FWD-ENV-T(Env)...>();
    }
  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] The member [`[*impls-for]<associate_t>::[*get-state]]
is initialized with a callable object equivalent to the following lambda:
[:zh_CN] 成员 [`[*impls-for]<associate_t>::[*get-state]] 以等价于如下 lambda 的
可调用对象初始化：

[codeblock]
[]<class Sndr, class Rcvr>(Sndr&& sndr, Rcvr& rcvr) noexcept([[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]) {
  auto&& [_, data] = std::forward<Sndr>(sndr);

  using associate_data_t = remove_cvref_t<decltype(data)>;
  using assoc_t = associate_data_t::[[redoc("*>")]]assoc-t;
  using sender_ref_t = associate_data_t::[[redoc("*>")]]sender-ref;

  using op_t = connect_result_t<typename sender_ref_t::element_type, Rcvr>;

  struct op_state {
    assoc_t [[redoc("*>")]]assoc;              // [=expos]
    union {
      Rcvr* [[redoc("*>")]]rcvr;               // [=expos]
      op_t [[redoc("*>")]]op;                  // [=expos]
    };

    explicit op_state(pair<assoc_t, sender_ref_t> parts, Rcvr& r)
      : [[redoc("*>")]]assoc(std::move(parts.first)) {
      if ([[redoc("*>")]]assoc) {
        ::new ([[redoc("^>")]]voidify([[redoc("*>")]]op)) op_t(connect(std::move(*parts.second), std::move(r)));
      } else {
        [[redoc("*>")]]rcvr = addressof(r);
      }
    }

    explicit op_state(associate_data_t&& ad, Rcvr& r)
      : op_state(std::move(ad).release(), r) {}

    explicit op_state(const associate_data_t& ad, Rcvr& r)
      requires [[redoc("`:c>")]]copy_constructible<associate_data_t>
      : op_state(associate_data_t(ad).release(), r) {}

    op_state(op_state&&) = delete;

    ~op_state() {
      if ([[redoc("*>")]]assoc) {
        [[redoc("*>")]]op.~op_t();
      }
    }

    void [[redoc("*>")]]run() noexcept {       // [=expos]
      if ([[redoc("*>")]]assoc) {
        start([[redoc("*>")]]op);
      } else {
        set_stopped(std::move(*[[redoc("*>")]]rcvr));
      }
    }
  };

  return op_state{std::forward_like<Sndr>(data), [[redoc("*>")]]rcvr};
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] The expression in the [`noexcept] clause of [`[*impls-for]<associate_t>::[*get-state]] is
[:zh_CN] [`[*impls-for]<associate_t>::[*get-state]] 的 [`noexcept] 子句中的表达式是
[codeblock]
(is_same_v<Sndr, remove_cvref_t<Sndr>> ||
 is_nothrow_constructible_v<remove_cvref_t<Sndr>, Sndr>) &&
[[redoc("*:c>")]]nothrow-callable<connect_t, [[redoc("*>")]]wrap-sender, Rcvr>
[codeblock:end]
[:en@~] where [*wrap-sender] is the type [`remove_cvref_t<[*data-type]<Sndr>>::[*wrap-sender]].
[:zh_CN@~] 其中 [*wrap-sender] 的类型为 [`remove_cvref_t<[*data-type]<Sndr>>::[*wrap-sender]]。

[para]
[:en] The member [`[*impls-for]<associate_t>::[*start]]
is initialized with a callable object equivalent to the following lambda:
[:zh_CN] 成员 [`[*impls-for]<associate_t>::[*start]] 以等价于如下 lambda 的可调用对象初始化：
[codeblock]
[](auto& state, auto&) noexcept -> void {
  state.[[redoc("*>")]]run();
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] The evaluation of [`associate(sndr, token)] may cause side effects
observable via [`token][=']s associated async scope object.
[:zh_CN] [`associate(sndr, token)] 的求值可能会导致通过 [`token] 的
关联异步作用域对象可观察的副作用。
